Rework the Set Action dialog's Mode/Recent/Simple coordination: Recent now stores (field, pattern) pairs and auto-switches to Simple mode for Simple-representable picks, the Mode toggle is always visible with Simple disabled when no preview is available, the complex-pattern notice has an inline Switch to Regex button, and mode/field/simple_op now persist independently per dialog entry point with a legacy-key fallback (#347, #348, #349, #351).
